data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom gem is the one you've been searching for. This property offers everything you could ever want in a home. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the beautiful brick accents in the living area, adding warmth and character to the space. The open floor plan creates an inviting and airy atmosphere, perfect for both relaxing  with your family and entertaining guests. The well-appointed kitchen will exceed your expectations with its ample counter space and plenty of storage. The three bedrooms are filled with natural light and offer plenty of room for your family to grow. The two bathrooms are both stylish and functional, ensuring convenience and comfort for everyone in the household. One of the highlights of this property is the large, fully fenced yard with a block wall in the backyard. This provides privacy and security while giving you plenty of space for outdoor activities. This property is ready for you to start creating your cherished memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and serenity this property has to offer. It won't be on the market for long, so act fast and make your homeownership dreams a reality!
